\f0\b0 \AppleTypeServices\AppleTypeServicesF65539 \strokec4  For a polymath, the challenge isn't a lack of skills; it's the fragmentation of those skills. ParadigmOS will be the lens that focuses that fragmentation into a single, inevitable point of impact.\
